languages.text: "Ты таков же, брат Торбальд, как и прежде — дерзок без меры, самодоволен и ведешь себя на чужой ладье будто хозяин".
"You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."
languages.original_text: "Ты таков же, брат Торбальд, как и прежде — дерзок без меры, самодоволен и ведешь себя на чужой ладье будто хозяин".

languages.text: “你可真是一点都没变啊，索巴德兄弟。你傲慢无礼、厚颜无耻，在别人的撞角长船上发号施令。”
languages.original_text: "You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."

traits.locale_text: “你可真是一点都没变啊，索巴德兄弟。你傲慢无礼、厚颜无耻，在别人的撞角长船上发号施令。”
traits.speaker: UlfarCompanion

languages.text: « Tu n'as pas changé, frère Thorbald. Toujours aussi arrogant et effronté, et tu te comportes sur ce drekkar comme si tu étais chez toi. »
languages.original_text: "You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."

traits.locale_text: « Tu n'as pas changé, frère Thorbald. Toujours aussi arrogant et effronté, et tu te comportes sur ce drekkar comme si tu étais chez toi. »
traits.speaker: UlfarCompanion

languages.text: 「変わらないな、同胞トールバルドよ…高慢で図々しく、他人のドレッカールの中でも我が物顔のように振舞う」
languages.original_text: "You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."

traits.locale_text: 「変わらないな、同胞トールバルドよ…高慢で図々しく、他人のドレッカールの中でも我が物顔のように振舞う」
traits.speaker: UlfarCompanion

languages.text: «Sigues igual, hermano Thorbald. Injusto y desvergonzado como siempre. Y te paseas por drekkares ajenos como si fueran tuyos».
languages.original_text: "You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."

traits.locale_text: «Sigue igual, hermano Thorbald. Arrogante y desvergonzado como siempre. Y te pasea por drekkares ajenos como si fueran tuyos».
traits.speaker: UlfarCompanion

languages.text: "Ihr habt Euch nicht verändert, Bruder Thorbald — hochnäsig und dreist über alle Maßen, und Ihr benehmt Euch auf dem Drekkar eines anderen, als wäre es Euer eigenes."
languages.original_text: "You have not changed, Brother Thorbald — high-handed and brazen without measure, and you carry yourself on another's drekkar like it is your own."

languages.text: "Hiç değişmemişsin Kardeş Thorbald. Ne küstahlığını ne pişkinliğini yitirmişsin, üstelik hâlâ başkasının drekkarını kendi malın gibi kullanıyorsun."
